description:
Start your own delivery business! Be the coolest boss around!
Everyone is hungry! Develop your own chain, and deliver everything from French fries to ice cream!
Transform your business from a humble service into a giant delivery business. The more deliveries you make, the more money you'll earn! Just don't run out of gas!
Delivery Dash is a casual strategy game in which the success of your business depends on your skills.
Highlights:
- Easy gameplay
- Lots of different tasks to keep you entertained
- Delightful animation and 3D graphics
